00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,660
Wait, you're game?

260
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:33,120
Awesome!

261
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:36,830
I'm going to get both of you 
soaking wet! Let's do this!

262
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:40,130
Um, are you sure about this?

263
00:13:40,130 --> 00:13:42,050
You can still get out of it...

264
00:13:42,350 --> 00:13:45,420
Are you seriously going to do it?

265
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:50,560
Well, I guess. As long as you're okay with it...

266
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:59,760
That's not a decision you can 
leave to someone else!

267
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:05,900
This isn't the kind of thing you do 
with anyone just because you're in the mood!

268
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:10,120
The basis has to be an emotional 
connection with someone you let into your heart!

269
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:14,840
Did you give up on college 
so you could do stuff like this?!

270
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,890
There's lots to do if you want to find work,

271
00:14:16,890 --> 00:14:19,080
like studying and acquiring qualifications!

272
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:21,540
I-I'm sorry!

273
00:14:21,540 --> 00:14:23,050
<i>The other day,</i>

274
00:14:23,050 --> 00:14:27,780
<i>someone kind of floated the idea 
of going to the same college together.</i>

275
00:14:28,260 --> 00:14:30,380
Wait, wait! It's not like that!

276
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:34,220
Kou-chan didn't want to play, 
but I basically forced him!

277
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:36,170
I saw the water fountain in the park,

278
00:14:36,170 --> 00:14:39,220
and I really wanted to have 
a water balloon battle again...

279
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:42,980
Water Balloons

280
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:42,980
They're a blast~!

281
00:14:46,470 --> 00:14:48,530
Wait a minute, are you Takane-chan?

282
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:51,500
Not sure which year it was in grade school,

283
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:53,230
but we used to be in PE together, right?

284
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,330
Don't you remember me?

285
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,620
It's Ellie.

286
00:14:56,390 --> 00:14:57,470
You're...

287
00:14:57,830 --> 00:15:01,170
The energetic girl who used 
to play with Shirota-kun a lot?

288
00:15:01,170 --> 00:15:02,740
Yes, yes!

289
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:04,380
But why are you whispering?

290
00:15:04,690 --> 00:15:07,370
Anyway, I ran into Kou-chan today,

291
00:15:07,370 --> 00:15:10,400
and I got nostalgic 
and forced him into this...

292
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:12,040
the water balloon battle.

293
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:14,350
I mean, I was into it, too.

294
00:15:14,890 --> 00:15:16,810
But as you said,

295
00:15:16,810 --> 00:15:21,010
maybe it's not the best look for
 high-schoolers to get soaked and fool around.

296
00:15:21,010 --> 00:15:23,310
Somebody might get the wrong idea.

297
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:25,010
That's true.

298
00:15:25,010 --> 00:15:27,030
Sorry, Takane-chan.

299
00:15:29,610 --> 00:15:33,980
There are people who will reprimand 
you without giving you a chance to explain, like so,

300
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:36,740
so you should refrain 
from taking careless actions.

301
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:40,330
<i>Wait, was I getting scolded 
over a hypothetical situation?</i>

302
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:44,080
Even if it's catching up with an old acquaintance,
you need to maintain decorum.

303
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:46,170
And now, please excuse me.

304
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:49,050
Wait, Takane-chan.

305
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:52,810
We just got together. Can't we talk a bit more?

306
00:15:52,810 --> 00:15:54,610
No, I...

307
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:56,680
Come on, it's fine.

308
00:15:56,680 --> 00:16:00,180
Hey, Kou-chan, could you go 
buy us something to drink?

309
00:16:00,180 --> 00:16:01,600
S-Sure...

310
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:10,040
I'm sorry, but I have somewhere to—

311
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,530
I'm sorry about before!

312
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:14,610
I went to all-girl middle and high schools,

313
00:16:14,610 --> 00:16:17,630
so I don't really know if I'm
being too familiar with boys.

314
00:16:17,630 --> 00:16:19,850
I was so happy about running into Kou-chan

315
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:22,580
that I kind of jumped on him 
as if we were still kids...

316
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:25,540
T-That's nothing to worry about.

317
00:16:25,540 --> 00:16:27,880
No, but it is!

318
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:28,830
I mean...

319
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:34,720
I wouldn't like it either, if someone 
got all close to the person I love.

320
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:36,430
What?

321
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:40,570
But man, you've gotten 
super cute, Takane-chan!

322
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:44,130
I mean you were always cute, 
but now you're more... pretty?

323
00:16:44,130 --> 00:16:46,400
Like, you've become beautiful.

324
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:48,380
You've also got this amazing aura.

325
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:51,860
Is it that thing where you get pretty 
when you're in love?

326
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:53,920
What are you even talking about?

327
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:56,030
I don't consider him to be more than a serva—

328
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:58,780
Sheesh, stop hiding it!

329
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:02,250
But that part of you is super cute, too!

330
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:06,840
You not knowing when you're being
too familiar isn't just with boys...

331
00:17:06,840 --> 00:17:08,650
What was that?

332
00:17:08,650 --> 00:17:09,960
Sorry for the wait.

333
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,920
I got some drinks and snacks.

334
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:15,680
Listen.

335
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:19,660
I won't try to stop whatever 
fantasies are in your head,

336
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:23,060
but please do not utter 
those baseless claims to anyone.

337
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:26,190
Huh? Ah, okay, okay! I won't tell anyone!

338
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:28,190
Oh! I'm so sorry.

339
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:30,180
I forgot I had a shoot coming up!

340
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:31,400
I've gotta get home!

341
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,250
What about the drinks?

342
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:35,430
You two have them.

343
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:38,160
Oh, and Kou-chan!

344
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,440
See you at cram school!

345
00:17:41,930 --> 00:17:43,140
Cram school?

346
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:45,320
Uh, well...

347
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:48,700
You're going to a cram school?

348
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:50,700
The same cram school as her?

349
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:53,970
Are you sure it's not a facility 
for training promiscuous women?

350
00:17:53,970 --> 00:17:56,470
How would I mistake that for a cram school?!

351
00:17:56,910 --> 00:18:01,390
Well, there's still a lot of problems 
I need to figure out, like tuition and such.

352
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:05,510
but it didn't sit right with me 
to give up before I tried.

353
00:18:05,510 --> 00:18:09,990
So, for starters, I signed up for the summer 
lessons that I can pay for with my own savings.

354
00:18:10,810 --> 00:18:15,030
Hoping that I can maybe 
go to the same school as you...

355
00:18:23,780 --> 00:18:27,410
Why didn't you discuss this with me?

356
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:29,560
I mean...

357
00:18:29,560 --> 00:18:31,230
It was a snap decision,

358
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:32,940
so there was no good time to mention it...

359
00:18:34,290 --> 00:18:40,160
It's annoying that natural-born 
slut found out before me.

360
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:45,060
It's true that you have no reliable 
income to pay for your tuition,

361
00:18:45,060 --> 00:18:47,010
and with your academic abilities,

362
00:18:47,010 --> 00:18:49,790
summer lessons will be a drop on a hot stone.

363
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:54,280
So you just recklessly 
sprung into action without a plan,

364
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,490
just to quell the feeling of unease...

365
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:59,620
Is what I'd normally say.

366
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:01,500
But regarding the tuition,

367
00:19:01,500 --> 00:19:04,910
by taking advantage of the university's 
financial aid and scholarships,

368
00:19:04,910 --> 00:19:08,580
you should be able to cover the rest 
with income from a part-time job.

369
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:12,050
That leaves the issue 
of your academic abilities.

370
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:14,180
There are no shortcuts in that regard.

371
00:19:15,610 --> 00:19:17,750
So I'll help you 
until the entrance exams.

372
00:19:18,650 --> 00:19:19,400
Wha?

373
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:21,850
I couldn't!

374
00:19:21,850 --> 00:19:24,130
I'm just doing this for my self-satisfaction...

375
00:19:24,130 --> 00:19:26,270
I don't want to be a bother.

376
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:17,600
I said that I would help you,

377
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,940
so you simply ought to say,
 "Thank you very much."

378
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:22,450
You redid it just for that?!

379
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:24,470
Here, the underwear.

380
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,220
Besides...

381
00:20:30,660 --> 00:20:32,720
It's not a bother.

382
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:42,620
I felt like doing something in return because 
you are trying to do something for me.

383
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,080
Now...

384
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:51,210
We're going to be busy.

385
00:20:52,260 --> 00:20:53,980
Don't just stand there.

386
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,220
We're going home.

387
00:21:02,910 --> 00:21:04,360
I'm going to work you so hard,

388
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:08,270
and then I'm going to work you 
further till your legs give out.

389
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:09,620
So you better prepare yourself.

390
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:12,050
You mean preparing 
for the entrance exam, right?!

391
00:21:12,050 --> 00:21:13,580
Of course.

392
00:21:13,580 --> 00:21:16,020
We only have so much time.

393
00:21:16,020 --> 00:21:18,910
Let's get the assignments for 
the summer break out of the way.

394
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:23,970
Shirota-kun.

395
00:21:23,970 --> 00:21:26,980
You have a really poor grasp of the basics.

396
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:29,050
I'm sorry.

397
00:21:29,430 --> 00:21:33,890
At this rate, you'll have trouble following
the lessons at cram school, will you not?

398
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:40,960
T-Temptation...

399
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,720
Hey!

400
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:44,190
Shirota-kun, focus on your assignments.

401
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:47,540
Kuro, you stop distracting him please.

402
00:21:53,450 --> 00:21:57,710
I can hardly believe he said 
he wants to go with me.

403
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:01,800
That is quite incredible,

404
00:22:01,800 --> 00:22:03,230
isn't it, Kuro?

